data.description: This stunning pool home is located in the beautiful gated community of Heatherwood in St Lucie West. This 4/2/2 home offers the perfect blend of comfort & style. Get ready to dive into a world of relaxation & luxury! Step into your own private paradise backyard, the sparkling pool is the centerpiece of this outdoor haven. This home's location is so convenient to golf courses, shopping, dining & entertainment. Everything you need is just a stone's throw away w/ easy access to the Turnpike & I-95. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your dream home. With its spacious interior, stunning outdoor space, & convenient location, it offers the perfect combination of comfort, style, & convenience. Dive into a life of luxury and relaxation today!
